# USING THE CLIENT

Use the following commands:

## MOVING THE CURSOR

Arrows: use them to move the cursors across the whole screen.

Page-up / Page-down: fastest horizontal movement.

Home / End: Place us at the beggining or the end of the board.

## BETS

Enter: Use ENTER to place a bet, bets are from 1 to 99, for bigger bets, use "1C" (100), "2C" (200), etc.

## EXIT

Esc: will exit the game in an elegant way, only during bet time and letting other clients that you have left the game.
